uk.ac.cam.darknet.common

Enum AttributeCategories

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<AttributeCategories>
      • uk.ac.cam.darknet.common.AttributeCategories
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<AttributeCategories>

    public enum AttributeCategories
extends java.lang.Enum<AttributeCategories>
    The set of attribute categories supported by the system. Each data collector provides a list of attributes it supports, indicating for each one which category it falls into.
    Author:
    Ibtehaj Nadeem
